episodes.title: Dear Ken 💙 A Plea from the Sidewalk
episodes.description:
This is me trying to speak directly to Ken. I really do think, deep down, you’re a good guy. I believe there are a lot of good people in that building who don’t belong trapped in there. This is my honest plea to you.

If you ever decide you’re ready to go… I’ll be right here, ready to scoot you out myself.

#DearKen
#AuditLA
#ItsACult
#scientology

episodes.title: Janet Weiland safe pointing the new D.A.
episodes.description: As I was filming the swearing in ceremony of the new D.A. Janet from another planet Weiland walks by after exiting the ceremony. Of course all of a sudden I was having connection issues. I guess Janet has a jammer. I hope she got the message that she is not wanted or welcomed here any longer.  Thank you Kristi for spotting her in the crowd. I missed the evil elf.
